ding to Matthew 16:17–18, Christ says more explicitly, ‘Blessed art thou, Simon Bar-jona … thou art Peter, and upon this rock I will build my church’. The name has been in continuous use since the Middle Ages."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Peter de Heveningham was born in 1137, in Heveningham, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom. He married Philippa Langley in 1156, in Heveningham, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in his hometown."},"et":{"1137–":"1137–Surnud","1139–Female":"1139–Surnud","1157–1191":"1157–1191","1137–Male":"1137–Surnud","1139":"1139","1137":"1137","1157":"1157","1156":"1156","1191":"1191","Heveningham, Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Heveningham, , Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1137–":"1137–Kuollut","1139–Female":"1139–Kuollut","1157–1191":"1157–1191","1137–Male":"1137–Kuollut","1139":"1139","1137":"1137","1157":"1157","1156":"1156","1191":"1191","Heveningham, Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Heveningham, , Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1137–":"1137–Décédé","1139–Female":"1139–Décédée","1157–1191":"1157–1191","1137–Male":"1137–Décédé","1139":"1139","1137":"1137","1157":"1157","1156":"1156","1191":"1191","Heveningham, Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Heveningham, , Suffolk, England":"Heveningham, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Peter de Heveningham est né en 1137, à Heveningham, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Philippa Langley en 1156, à Heveningham, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1137–":"1137–Verstorben","1139–Female":"1139–Verstorben","1157–1191":"1157–1191","1137–Male":"1137–Verstorben","1139":"1139","1137":"1137","1157":"1157","1156":"1156","1191":"1191","Heveningham, Suffolk, En